      <h3>Data Mart Search Parameters</h3>
	  
      <p>DAF Marts SHALL support the following common parameters as part of queries related to DAF-Research profiles:</p>
	  
      <ul>
	     
        <li>
          <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#id">_id</a>
        </li>
		 
        <li>
          <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#lastUpdated">_lastUpdated</a>
        </li>
		 
        <li>
          <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#profile">_profile</a>
        </li>
		 
        <li>
          <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#count">_count</a>
        </li>
		 
        <li>
          <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#include">_include</a>
        </li>
	  
      </ul>
	 
      <p>Data Marts SHALL support the following search contexts defined within the 
        <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#Introduction">FHIR</a>specification.
      </p> 
	
      <ul>
		
        <li>Search context by specifying a particular resource type</li>
	
      </ul>
	
      <p>Data Marts SHALL support 
        <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#Modifiers">Modifiers</a> as applicable to the data types of the search parameters. Data Marts SHALL also support 
        <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#Composite Search Parameters">Composite Search Parameters</a> as defined in the FHIR specification.
      </p>
	  
